## OpenE2EE — mobile/android — gitignore (combined from PR-22a Android VPN +
## Sprint 3 §9 native dev tooling + Sprint 5 PR-28 Android Gradle config)

# Anything produced by `flutter pub get`, `flutter analyze`, the Android
# Gradle Plugin, or `flutter build apk` should NOT be checked in.
#
# PR-28 (Sprint 5) lands the full Gradle build config: `settings.gradle.kts`,
# root `build.gradle.kts`, `app/build.gradle.kts`, and
# `gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.properties` are all committed. The files
# in the .gitignore rules below (build outputs, the wrapper JAR binary,
# GeneratedPluginRegistrant, IDE caches, keystores) remain generated or
# developer-local and MUST stay out of source control.

# Local machine config — points at the developer's Flutter SDK.
local.properties

# Gradle wrapper distribution / caches / wrapper jar (not yet committed).
gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar
.gradle/
.gradle
**/build/
app/build/
captures/
**/.cxx/

# Flutter / Dart auto-generated plugin registration — regenerated on
# every `flutter pub get` / `flutter analyze` / `flutter build`. Never
# hand-edit. Kept out of git until the Gradle build is wired up.
**/GeneratedPluginRegistrant.java
**/GeneratedPluginRegistrant.kt
.kotlin/

# IDE caches inside android/
.idea/
.kotlin/

# Keystores / signing material — never commit. Belt-and-braces; the
# VpnService does NOT require signing for the sampling path.
*.jks
*.keystore

# Native dev tooling (Sprint 3 §9)
# Android Studio IDE folder (kept out; .idea/ at repo root handled separately)
**/.idea/
**/.idea/workspace.xml
**/.idea/tasks.xml
**/.idea/gradle.xml
**/.idea/assetWizardSettings.xml
**/.idea/dictionaries
**/.idea/shelf
**/.idea/libraries
**/.idea/caches
**/.idea/modules.xml
**/.idea/navEditor.xml

# Native build outputs
.cxx/
build/
**/build/
captures/
.externalNativeBuild/
.cxx/

# Local config
local.properties
**/local.properties

# Debug / release keystores
*.jks
*.keystore
*.p12
*.cer
release.keystore
debug.keystore

# ProGuard mapping files (regenerated)
**/*.mapping

# Crashlytics / Firebase
fabric.properties
google-services.json

# Fastlane
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/screenshots
fastlane/test_output
fastlane/readme.md

# Logs
*.log
*.hprof